text: Somethin' Bout Love is the third studio album of keyboardist Brian Culbertson released in 1999 on Atlantic/WEA Records. The album reached No. 3 on the Billboard Contemporary Jazz Albums chart and No. 8 on the Billboard Top Jazz Albums chart. ==Singles== Get'n Over You got to No. 16 on the Billboard Adult R&B; Songs chart. I'm Gonna Miss You also reached No. 21 on the Billboard Adult R&B; Songs chart. ==Tracklisting== ==References== Category:1999 albums Category:Atlantic Records albums
title: Somethin' Bout Love
